Package: tubecleanR
Type: Package
Title: Parsing and Preprocessing YouTube Comment Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-02-26
Authors@R: c(person("Julian", "Kohne", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "julian.kohne@gesis.org",comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6710-7545")),
             person("Johannes", "Breuer", role = "aut", email = "johannes.breuer@cais-research.de",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5906-7873")))
Maintainer: Julian Kohne <julian.kohne@gesis.org>
Description: This mini-package is meant as extension for the tuber and the vosonSML packages for preprocessing user comments collected via the YouTube API. The preprocessing in this package focuses on links, emoticons, emoji, video timestamps, and user names. The output of the main function of this package creates a well-defined dataframe suitable for further processing and (text) analysis.
Imports: anytime, qdapRegex, stringi, utils
